    Service, Coprocessor, RegionCoprocessor

    public class ColumnAggregationEndpointWithErrors
extends org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor.protobuf.generated.ColumnAggregationWithErrorsProtos.ColumnAggregationServiceWithErrors
implements RegionCoprocessor
    Test coprocessor endpoint that always throws a DoNotRetryIOException for requests on the last region in the table. This allows tests to ensure correct error handling of coprocessor endpoints throwing exceptions.
